data.description: This beautiful home features a split floor plan with three bedrooms and two baths with NO Carpet !  Large living room with wood burning fireplace. The large primary bedroom flows into a spa bathroom with a large whirl pool tub and separate shower.  The oversized closet is a dream! Across the home you will find two additional bedrooms and a guest bath.   You will love the shed in the backyard for storage.  Large Fenced in backyard  Don't wait! Make your  appointment today!
